cost more than the ring.

07:41.035 --> 07:42.755
- Right, right, right.
- You know, you feel that?

07:42.805 --> 07:45.655
The best 50 pesos I spent. Shit.

07:45.705 --> 07:47.765
Hey, where's Papa D?

07:47.815 --> 07:49.365
He said he don't need a haircut.

07:49.415 --> 07:50.725
You serious?

07:50.775 --> 07:52.035
Never known that man to go to a party

07:52.085 --> 07:53.565
without a shave and a fresh cut.

07:53.615 --> 07:55.365
Well, he's not coming to the pour.

07:55.415 --> 07:56.865
